VII. PRAYER & CONCLUSION
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

The prosecution is trying to build a fortress of criminality upon a foundation 
of scientific sand. When the standard used (IS 1199:2018) is wrong, the sampling 
condition (storm) is invalid, and the procedure (ex-parte) is illegal, there 
remains NO evidence in the eyes of the law.

[Prayer maintained as per v4, with added emphasis on the Inapplicability of FSL
report due to wrong standard selection.]

